I.u[9785] = {n:"Rushu\'s Shushu",t:18,d:"This demon will accompany you throughout all of your wandering, from the Astrub Zaap to the cemetery and maybe even to the cemetery from the Astrub Zaap. It is also full of bitter hatred for Ouassingues... it\'s a long story, but it has something to do with a dirty floor and a bucket of hot water. If you attack a Ouassingue, this demon will be happy to help!",ep:0,g:52,l:1,wd:true,fm:true,w:10,c:"PZ=1",p:1};
